^ Local time.

^ For some countries it is unclear whether they report samples or cases. One person tested twice is recorded as one case and two samples.

^ Excluding Greenland and the Faroe Islands.

^ Northern Cyprus is not recognized as a sovereign state by any country except Turkey.

^ Includes data for Liechtenstein.

^ Not a United Nations member.
